# ⏰ Alarm by Madhuri

A clean and minimal web-based alarm clock built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.

## 🔥 Features

- ⏱️ Live Digital Clock
- ⏰ Set Alarm with Custom Title
- 🔊 Upload Your Own Alarm Sound
- 🛑 Stop Alarm & Test Sound Feature
- 📱 Responsive UI with sleek dark mode

